---
---

<section class="one-nation-video-section" id="video-presentation" aria-labelledby="video-section-title">
	<div class="one-nation-video-container">

		<div class="one-nation-video-text">
			<p class="one-nation-video-label">One Nation Agency</p>
			<h2 id="video-section-title" class="one-nation-video-title">Communication stratégique, innovation et influence</h2>
			<p class="one-nation-video-desc">
				Découvrez notre vision d'une communication sur mesure, à la croisée du conseil stratégique, de l'innovation et des nouveaux usages, notamment à travers les agents IA.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="one-nation-video-wrapper">
			<video
				class="one-nation-video-player"
				controls
				muted
				preload="metadata"
				playsinline
				aria-label="Présentation One Nation Agency"
			>
				<source src="/presentationOneNation.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
				<p>Votre navigateur ne supporte pas la lecture vidéo. <a href="/presentationOneNation.mp4">Télécharger la vidéo</a>.</p>
			</video>
		</div>

		<div class="one-nation-video-cta">
			<a href="/contact" class="one-nation-video-btn">Nous contacter</a>
		</div>

	</div>
</section>

<section class="vision" id="vision">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="hero-section">
			<img src="/conseils.jpg" alt="Vision d'entreprise" class="hero-image">
			<div class="hero-overlay"></div>
			<h2>Notre Vision et nos Valeurs</h2>
		</div>
		<p class="intro-text">Chez One Nation, nos valeurs fondamentales guident chacune de nos actions et façonnent notre approche unique de la communication stratégique. Elles représentent l'essence même de notre identité et de notre engagement envers nos clients.</p>
		
		<div class="values">
			<h3>Nos Valeurs</h3>
			<div class="values-grid">
				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="icon">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
							<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
							<line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
							<line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"></line>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h4>Vision</h4>
					<p>Être un partenaire stratégique incontournable pour renforcer l'impact des institutions et créer des changements positifs durables.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="icon">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
							<polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h4>Excellence</h4>
					<p>Viser constamment les plus hauts standards de qualité dans tous nos services.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="icon">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
							<path d="M12 19l7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z"></path>
							<path d="M18 13l-1.5-7.5L2 2l3.5 14.5L13 18l5-5z"></path>
							<path d="M2 2l7.586 7.586"></path>
							<circle cx="11" cy="11" r="2"></circle>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h4>Innovation</h4>
					<p>Développer des solutions créatives et avant-gardistes pour répondre aux défis complexes de communication.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="icon">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
							<path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"></path>
							<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h4>Transparence</h4>
					<p>Maintenir une communication ouverte et honnête avec nos clients et parties prenantes.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="icon">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
  					<path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm5.93 6.36l-1.42 1.42c-.2.2-.51.2-.71 0l-1.41-1.41c-.2-.2-.2-.51 0-.71l1.41-1.41c.2-.2.51-.2.71 0l1.42 1.42c.2.2.2.51 0 .71zm-3.54 3.54l-1.41 1.41c-.2.2-.51.2-.71 0l-1.41-1.41c-.2-.2-.2-.51 0-.71l1.41-1.41c.2-.2.51-.2.71 0l1.41 1.41c.2.2.2.51 0 .71zm-3.54 3.54l-1.41 1.41c-.2.2-.51.2-.71 0l-1.41-1.41c-.2-.2-.2-.51 0-.71l1.41-1.41c.2-.2.51-.2.71 0l1.41 1.41c.2.2.2.51 0 .71zm-3.54-3.54l-1.41 1.41c-.2.2-.51.2-.71 0l-1.41-1.41c-.2-.2-.2-.51 0-.71l1.41-1.41c.2-.2.51-.2.71 0l1.41 1.41c.2.2.2.51 0 .71zm3.54-3.54l-1.41 1.41c-.2.2-.51.2-.71 0l-1.41-1.41c-.2-.2-.2-.51 0-.71l1.41-1.41c.2-.2.51-.2.71 0l1.41 1.41c.2.2.2.51 0 .71z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h4>Investissement</h4>
					<p>S'engager pleinement dans chaque projet avec éthique et professionnalisme.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	/* ── Section vidéo ── */
	.one-nation-video-section {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(175, 175, 174, 0.15);
	}

	.one-nation-video-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.one-nation-video-text {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 720px;
	}

	.one-nation-video-label {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
	}

	.one-nation-video-title {
		font-size: 2.2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-white);
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.one-nation-video-desc {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.one-nation-video-wrapper {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 900px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
		background: #000;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
	}

	.one-nation-video-player {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: #000;
	}

	.one-nation-video-cta {
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	.one-nation-video-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		background: var(--color-accent);
		color: var(--color-background);
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.one-nation-video-btn:hover {
		background: var(--color-white);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.one-nation-video-section {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}

		.one-nation-video-title {
			font-size: 1.6rem;
		}

		.one-nation-video-desc {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
		}

		.one-nation-video-btn {
			padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
			font-size: 0.95rem;
		}
	}

	/* ── Section vision existante (inchangée) ── */
	.vision {
		padding: 0 0 8rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.hero-section {
		position: relative;
		height: 400px;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero-image {
		position: absolute;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		filter: brightness(0.3);
	}

	.hero-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(rgba(72, 71, 68, 0.7), rgba(72, 71, 68, 0.9));
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-white);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
	}

	.intro-text {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
		padding: 0 2rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.values {
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	h3 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.values-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.value-card {
		background: rgba(175, 175, 174, 0.1);
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.value-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		background: rgba(175, 175, 174, 0.15);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.icon {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.value-card:hover .icon {
		transform: scale(1.1);
	}

	h4 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		color: var(--color-white);
	}

	p {
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero-section {
			height: 300px;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			padding: 0 1rem;
		}

		.intro-text {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			padding: 0 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
